  "body": "\r\n# ðŸš€ Feature Request\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nAbout this part of the doc : \r\n \r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1905292/96283458-88f65980-0fdc-11eb-8b05-61b43122d725.png)\r\n\r\nQuick feedback on that part : I tried to set `--http-web3provider=localhost`, then `--http-web3provider=127.0.0.1`. Took me a while to realize that the full string was required (`--http-web3provider=http://localhost:8545`).\r\n\r\n### Describe the solution you'd like\r\n\r\n- The most trivial solution is to update the doc so people like me can understand what is the required string format.\r\n- Another solution is to assume that HTTP is used by default - and eventually using the default port when not specified. The risk of using default values is to connect to the wrong node when an user runs multiple `geth` instances.",
